# Kingsway — environment variables (TEMPLATE — no real secrets here).
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. The scaffold builds/renders without these; each is
# only required when its feature runs (PRD §7 — zero live keys needed to scaffold).
# NEVER put real keys in this file — it is committed to git.

# --- Supabase (Postgres, admin auth) ---
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# Server-only. Bypasses RLS — used by API route handlers. NEVER expose to the browser.
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# --- Resend (transactional email + open tracking + .ics) ---
RESEND_API_KEY=
# From identity used across all templates (PRD §4.4). Optional; has a placeholder default.
KINGSWAY_EMAIL_FROM=

# --- App ---
# Public base URL, used in email links and .ics (e.g. https://kingsway.example).
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Founder's WhatsApp — a wa.link short link or an E.164 number (see lib/whatsapp.ts).
NEXT_PUBLIC_FOUNDER_WHATSAPP=

# Footer social links (optional — a link only appears once its URL is set). See lib/social.ts.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUBSTACK_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_X_URL=
